n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2295%2c20221208%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,2295,20221208,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2295","JDATE":"20221208","JTITLE":"竊盜"}